      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a decent start for the general outline, but the information density is honestly pretty low. The score on my end came back quite low because while you hit the big milestones, there's a lot of generic filler text.\n\nI need this to be much more detailed for the textbook. Can you expand this into a more comprehensive summary? Try to weave in more specifics—actual political figures, key committees, specific battles, or even specific legislative acts—to get that density up. \n\nRemember, I still need it to be a readable story for students, so please don't just dump a list of names. I'm looking for a dense, professional historical narrative.",
